en_697874_0	Four people who have fallen ill suddenly during a party at a hotel in Wadduwa area, have been admitted to the Panadura Base Hospital.Three of them have died.
en_697874_1	The other person is also reported to be in a critical condition.
en_697874_2	About 1,500 people have attended the party.
en_697874_3	The reports say they have come to know each other over the internet.
en_697874_4	The party has been organized by an institution in the Kaduwela area.
en_697874_5	The Wadduwa police are conducting further investigations into the incident.
